Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.82,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:9989,13826}I can feel the sunshine on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:13826,17121}I think I'll bask in it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:22.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:18122,22126}It's a beginning of a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.46,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25338,28466}That's the moment I like the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.51,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29342,33513}the one that starts it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:33513,36849}Something lovely is about to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.72,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:36849,40728}I just have a hunch like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.40,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:40728,48403}Woom! My reflection the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.28,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:48403,52282}Woom! Looks rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:56.03,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:52282,56035}It feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:02.87,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56035,62875}I reach out to the clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:10.67,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:63793,70675}I'm so excited and filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:15.09,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:71467,75096}Love, work, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:46.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103082,106002}It's nice to walk in the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:49.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106210,109631}I've heard that trees produce\Nelements which relax people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:53.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110882,113009}The girls who are tired\Nof the business of urban life…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:55.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113092,115553}…are resting for a minute,\NI suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:58.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115928,118264}Hey! Why don't we\Nrace to that tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:01:59.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118473,119599}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:01.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119891,121851}Are you ready? Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:10.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129359,130943}First place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:25.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142246,145041}Man! I don't know if you're\Ntired from playing or what…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:27.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145249,147293}…but aren't you\Nmissing the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:29.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147418,149253}We're on the mountain…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:30.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149337,150630}…behind the school\Nto observe nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:31.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150755,151756}But we are still in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:33.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152298,153758}Mr. Yamano is amazed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:44.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159931,164268}A PRECIOUS\NCREATURE OF NATURE:\NSAVE THE BEAUTIFUL BUTTERFLY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:54.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173444,174570}It's like…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:57.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174737,177615}…when you put out cotton\Nsoaked in sugar water…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:00.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178157,180284}…then different\Ninsects gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:03.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180827,183413}Here, in particular, there are\Nmany varieties of butterflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:12.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191629,192630}Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192797,194507}I wonder what those\Nbutterflies are called.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194757,196259}Aren't they swallowtails\Nor something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:19.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196759,199387}They look a little\Ndifferent to me…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200179,202598}They're called\NYamano Oomurasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202724,204475}Yamano Oomurasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204934,206894}It's the same name\Nas yours, Mr. Yamano.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207687,209230}As a matter of fact,\Nthirty years ago…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209397,211733}…I discovered that butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221659,223077}The first time I saw it was…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:45.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223244,225663}…when I had just come\Nto this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242513,243514}Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:05.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244056,245641}"Yamano Oomurasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:09.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246058,249729}Discovered by\NMr. Ikutaro Yamano in 1966.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249854,252940}Found in a few small areas\Nlike Seika City."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:16.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253566,256194}At that time there was\Na lot of green around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256277,257612}But the groves\Naround here…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:18.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257737,258946}…have been\Ndestroyed one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259197,261157}Now we can only see\NYamano Oomurasaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:23.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261365,263951}…right here\Nin the forest of St. Paulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264243,265536}Poor things…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:28.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265995,268039}But it's not all bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:31.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268372,271459}A few years ago,\Na law was passed…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271584,273419}…which prohibits taking\Nany insects from this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273669,275087}Can you guys hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:54.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291979,294148}Mr. Yamano has a butterfly\Nnamed after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294315,295983}He's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:57.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296108,297193}He deserves his position…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297360,298528}…as the special advisor\Nhere at St. Paulia Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:04:59.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298736,299862}He's super nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:02.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300154,302406}What's that? I heard\N"great" and "super nice."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302532,304200}Is someone\Ntalking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:07.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305076,307745}Is it Haneoka or Mimori?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309580,311207}Hey! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312875,314877}Start cleaning\Nlike you're supposed to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314961,317463}If you don't, I'll be scolded\Nas the group leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317797,320299}All right. I understand,\NGroup Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:24.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321551,324470}Hey, Takamiya. You, too,\Ncome here and help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:26.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325137,326681}All right…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331811,333312}Bagworm…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335648,337567}The bagworm scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343281,345408}Asuka! I was scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:46.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345491,346826}Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347118,348953}It's hard to believe\Nthat Takamiya has…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:50.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349036,350705}…something she's afraid of…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:51.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350872,351956}Right, Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:59.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356043,359797}Hey, what kind\Nof insect don't you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360298,362341}I suppose… ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:05.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364343,365344}How about you, Kyoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365428,366679}For me it's a mantis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:11.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368472,371183}I just can't stand that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371392,373519}What don't you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:16.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374270,376439}– Well…\N– Yours must be this…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:17.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376689,377690}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:23.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382612,383613}Oh, shoot…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383738,385239}Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:39.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396542,399420}You boiled the pasta\Ntoo long today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:40.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399754,400963}If you're going to complain…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401088,402924}…why don't you cook\Nonce in a while?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403633,405635}And what happened\Nto your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:47.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405760,407011}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407470,408763}It's a girlfriend, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409847,411057}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:52.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411724,412725}I remember when…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412850,414518}…great-great-grandfather\Nwould tell us…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:57.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414810,417229}…that we're a family who\Nhas trouble with women.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:59.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417396,419106}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426113,428240}Oh, shoot. I did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428783,430785}He must be very angry now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433496,435289}Hey, Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:05.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484130,485423}Mr. Yamano…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:07.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487008,487967}Mimori…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:14.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490720,494015}You can't find a single\NYamano Oomurasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:17.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495349,497018}Who would do\Nsuch a terrible thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498060,500021}I hate to accuse anyone…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:22.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500563,502606}…but I can guess who did it…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:28.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504817,508654}About a week ago,\Ntwo young men visited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:33.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510281,513409}So you want to collect\Na Yamano Oomurasaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:37.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513659,517580}…in the forest of St. Paulia, right?\NIt's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518164,520624}This is a protected habitat\Nfor the Yamano Oomurasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521125,523294}The law prohibits\Ntheir collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524045,526922}So why don't you\Ngive up and go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527089,530718}Mr. Yamano,\Nwe already knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:53.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530926,533429}That's why we came here\Nto discuss it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:57.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534472,537558}How about just a few?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:59.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537683,539101}No one would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:00.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539310,540936}I won't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:06.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543564,546942}Idiots!\NDon't come back again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:13.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549487,553449}I suppose they did it\Nas revenge for my refusal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554825,557036}Mimori, no, Sister…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557578,559789}Will you hear my prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:20.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559914,560873}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:24.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561957,564919}Could you ask God,\Nwith me…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565795,567379}…that those butterflies…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:30.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567588,570508}…will return to the forest\Nof St. Paulia again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:32.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570966,572051}Mr. Yamano…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:41.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580976,581936}That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582228,583896}I investigated…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:46.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584063,586232}…and discovered that\NMr. Yamano was correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:48.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586941,588734}The two men,\NYoshiyuki Ishida…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588901,590402}…and Kenichi Kawai live in\Na European-style building…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590569,592071}…on Seventh Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592613,594073}On the surface they pretend…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594198,595950}…to be regular\Nbutterfly collectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:57.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596200,597201}But behind the scenes…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:58.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597326,598452}…they're selling rare butterflies…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598577,600788}…which are illegal to catch,\Nand fetch a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601163,603624}Good job, Seira!\NA wonderful investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:07.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604208,607044}So what happened\Nto the Yamano Oomurasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:08.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607211,608170}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:11.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608379,611132}The men are still hiding\Nthe butterflies in their house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:12.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611632,612675}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:14.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612842,614218}For Mr. Yamano's sake…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614385,616595}…please get\Nthe Yamano Oomurasaki back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617721,618722}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:21.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619056,621267}Those men are enemies\Nof the entire earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622059,624812}St. Tail will teach them\Na harsh lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:31.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627982,631610}NIKO NIKO MART\NFRESH-MADE OMUSUBI
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:39.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638534,639994}Shoot! It's a miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:41.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640369,641704}How about yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:43.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642079,643414}Mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:46.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644248,646250}Asuka, how about yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648878,651589}"Tonight I'll take\Nthe Yamano Oomurasaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:53.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651672,653883}…from the Ishida residence\Non Seventh Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:54.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654008,654967}– St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:56.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655342,656760}It's a warning note!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:01.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658470,661557}I licked St. Tail's\Nwarning note…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661682,664018}– Let me lick it, too!\N– Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:05.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664101,665811}What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671901,673277}Eimi, can you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:14.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673402,674361}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:19.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678490,679909}I've just had an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680159,681785}For the opening\Nof my next magic show…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:23.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681952,683829}…how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684663,686415}Oh, are doves coming out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686665,688459}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:33.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692338,693756}Wow! Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694381,695549}Really, Eimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:36.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695633,696842}Yes, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:39.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696967,699678}I'm sure your next show is\Ngoing to be another success!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701055,702139}Eimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:44.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702723,704099}Genichiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:58.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716278,718113}It's really embarrassing…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:00.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719323,720699}Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720866,722576}It's a little early,\Nbut I guess I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723702,725913}Ruby, cover for me\Nwhile I'm gone!
Comment: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:09.75,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:729750,729750}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:14.75,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:734755,734755}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:22.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739176,742721}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748060,749228}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:32.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751438,752523}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:37.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754733,757152}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:53.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770499,773168}Meimi, tonight you're\Ndealing with butterflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773419,774962}Please be more\Ncareful than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775254,776922}Yes. You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:02.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779800,782845}May the blessings\Nof God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:28.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806452,808954}Ishida, are they\Nthat interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:30.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809121,810539}They're just butterflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:32.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810706,812374}Just butterflies?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:34.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812750,814168}These are some\Nof the last in the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:35.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814293,815753}They're Yamano Oomurasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:39.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816253,819548}Look at these beautiful,\Ncolorful patterns and shapes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:42.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819840,822593}They are jewels\Nmade by the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:45.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823969,825846}Sir, you have guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826347,828140}Who's here at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828307,830184}He said he's Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:51.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830559,831852}Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832603,833854}Is it the Asuka Jr. …
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834021,835481}…who is the special\Ninvestigator of St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:56.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835647,836607}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:58.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837524,838484}That means…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838734,840652}…St. Tail is after them…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841403,842571}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843113,844573}Without any evidence…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:06.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844740,846825}…no one can do anything to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:09.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847659,849536}All right. Tell him\Nwe'll be with him in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:10.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849703,850704}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:16.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853457,856710}If they discover\Nthese here, I'll be…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857211,858420}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:20.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858587,860339}We'll hide them\Nin the usual place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:30.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867513,870057}Are you Asuka Jr.?\NWhat's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871308,872559}St. Tail warned us…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:35.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872684,875020}…that she will steal some\NYamano Oomurasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875145,876188}Where are the butterflies?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877147,878774}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:42.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879233,882611}We don't have those\Nbutterflies in our collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882986,884238}Anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884363,885489}Nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:50.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886240,890035}It is true that our hobby\Nis collecting butterflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:55.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890828,895457}But it's illegal to catch\Na Yamano Oomurasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:58.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895749,898419}There is no way\Nwe would have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:00.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899128,900879}So you're sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:02.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900963,902131}…that there aren't…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:03.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902339,903715}…any Yamano Oomurasaki\Nin this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904258,905467}I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905843,907094}If you don't believe us…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907219,908762}…why don't you\Nsearch the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:24.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921733,924403}There's a pool…\NThey live in a mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:26.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924820,926447}He inherited it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:29.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927948,929116}How is your search going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:30.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929825,930909}Well, Asuka Jr. …
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931076,933662}We haven't seen\Na single butterfly outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:37.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934037,937249}I see. That's enough out here.\NPlease help us inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:38.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937458,938417}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944256,946967}I have to fiind the butterflies\Nbefore Asuka Jr. does.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950596,953140}Where on earth\Nare they hiding them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:58.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957478,958479}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959188,961482}Asuka Jr., we haven't\Nfound any on the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961607,963358}There aren't any\Non the second floor or in the attic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964234,965486}Why don't you admit…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965569,968280}…that you've made\Na mistake, Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:09.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968530,969656}It can't be right…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970032,971241}It's impossible…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:13.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971366,973744}…that St. Tail would send\Na fake warning note.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974745,977498}Rather than listening\Nto the words of a citizen…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977623,979666}…you trust the words of a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:24.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980959,984087}How rude! I told the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:26.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985964,986924}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992513,993472}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995098,997809}…Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:39.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998727,999978}…Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:54.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012366,1014117}It's the butterflies' curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:57.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014451,1017246}I'm not deceived\Nby this illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:02.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021792,1022793}Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023460,1025587}I came to pick up\Nthe Yamano Oomurasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:08.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026046,1028632}St. Tail! Battle with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:10.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029424,1030551}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:11.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030676,1031718}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:12.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031802,1032886}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044690,1046149}Yamano Oomurasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:28.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046275,1048485}We searched everywhere,\Nand we couldn't find them…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048986,1050237}There's a difference out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:31.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050320,1051321}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052072,1053490}That's what I said…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:36.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053740,1056660}…but I just saw the reflection\Nof the wings by the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059788,1061164}They're my butterflies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:42.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061290,1062332}Give them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062416,1064042}Arrest these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:50.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069172,1070966}I'm taking these butterflies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:53.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071383,1073010}I won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:01.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079600,1081018}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090527,1092738}He definitely did a belly flop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:15.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094364,1095490}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:19.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096283,1099620}Shut up! Next time\NI'll definitely catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:20.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099745,1100704}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:16.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153215,1156134}God, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:30.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169856,1170816}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:31.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170941,1171900}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:34.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172567,1174861}Oh, I wonder what it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:43.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180409,1183620}"St. Tail shows up\Nat the butterfly mansion!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:45.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184496,1185956}Good morning, Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:49.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186081,1189042}Look at my big scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:53.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189334,1193714}So it was the same people\Nwho damaged our mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194089,1196049}Besides the Yamano Oomurasaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:58.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196133,1198510}…those men were selling\Nother butterflies, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:02.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199136,1202055}Mr. Yamano must\Nbe relieved now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:05.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202597,1205058}By the way, Sawatari…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:07.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205308,1207811}…don't you have\Nsome other big news?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:10.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208270,1210856}Women's intuition\Nis very sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:13.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211356,1213608}As a matter of fact, although\NI didn't put it in the article…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:17.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213859,1217070}…the best scoop from last night\Nis this photograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:19.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217738,1219865}You mean the real\Nidentity of St. Tail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:21.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220574,1221700}I wonder…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221783,1223243}Let me see! Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:27.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226246,1227289}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230333,1232002}What is it?\NAn exclusive photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234421,1235756}Let me see, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:38.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237799,1238759}Saruwatari…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:43.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240677,1243513}I didn't take that photo…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:44.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243638,1244639}…but my acquaintance…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244890,1246141}…happened to have a camera…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246266,1247267}Saruwatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:50.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247893,1250687}Boy…\NOh, a butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251271,1252939}Ah-cho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:54.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253273,1254858}Wait a minute!
